metadata.name: The Nalezhe Collection
metadata.description:
Alter ego to Abraham Joseph, "Nalezhe Geauvore" is the identity AbJo assumes when he writes his most baroque, bouncey, yet intricate and meticulous compositions, among many other expressions not commonly associated with Ab’s usually effortlessly artful sample chopping and loop work. These are two samples of the collection of "Nalezhe's" inspirations, curated to fit the vibe of the AbJonian Vault Selections, a special offering to AbJo’s most respected and loyal collectors and supporters...  
  
Samples included in this Kit:  
 - TNC_Beethoven's Slap_C#_104 BPM  
 - TNC_Momentum_C_136 BPM
